 groups in the Philippines]]\n[[Category:Filipino people of Chinese descent]]\n[[Category:Mestizo]]\n", "name_user": "Juanmakabulos", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eColonial caste system", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Filipino_mestizo"}
